                      </Style>
                      <ZIndex>9</ZIndex>
                      <CanGrow>true</CanGrow>
                      <Value>="1.  Payment shall be made by Cash or DD in favour of ‘NOIDA’ directly in HDFC &amp; ICICI Bank any branches of Noida or Online-Payment can be via official website of Noida Jal i.e. www.noidajalonline.com ."+ System.Environment.NewLine + System.Environment.NewLine +"2.  If amount has already been deposited then,The demand is treated as withdrawn."+ System.Environment.NewLine + System.Environment.NewLine +"3.  The water connection shall be disconnected if payment is not made upto due date without any further notice."+ System.Environment.NewLine + System.Environment.NewLine +"4.  For any Clarification / error please contact to the office of the Project Engineer water work's compound "+Fields!Div_type.Value+" between 11.00 a.m. to 2.00 p.m. on all working days"+ System.Environment.NewLine + System.Environment.NewLine +"5.  This is  a computer generated demand which requires no signature."+ System.Environment.NewLine + System.Environment.NewLine +"6. For any other information visit the WebSite http://noidaauthorityonline.com ."+ System.Environment.NewLine + System.Environment.NewLine +"7. E &amp; O E."</Value>
